Rich guys. Conventional.

50:00.380 --> 50:01.460
It's a problem.

50:01.500 --> 50:03.780
Then there was Angelo.

50:04.900 --> 50:06.420
Twenty-five years old...

50:06.500 --> 50:07.940
handsome, healthy...

50:08.020 --> 50:09.700
exciting...

50:09.780 --> 50:11.620
sophisticated.

50:11.700 --> 50:12.780
Considerate.

50:18.380 --> 50:19.460
So?

50:21.620 --> 50:23.420
Well, I think
that we just sort of, um...

50:24.980 --> 50:27.060
grew apart as people.

50:31.300 --> 50:33.260
The aerobics instructor?

50:36.620 --> 50:38.660
Like I said...

50:38.740 --> 50:41.060
it's a common scenario.

50:44.260 --> 50:45.700
So who was next?

50:45.780 --> 50:48.780
Then I started getting
problems with my teeth.

50:48.860 --> 50:50.420
With your teeth?

50:50.500 --> 50:52.340
Yeah, my teeth.

50:54.340 --> 50:55.460
Hey, want a ride?

50:55.540 --> 50:57.340
Hi, thanks for stopping, guys.

50:57.380 --> 51:00.100
Uh, we're not stealing it,
we're just borrowing it.

51:00.180 --> 51:01.980
Had that dream again last night.

51:02.020 --> 51:03.700
What dream?

51:03.780 --> 51:05.940
We were
on that game show Perfect Love.

51:06.020 --> 51:08.380
- Mmm. Fascinating.
- And my life was in danger.

51:08.420 --> 51:09.460
On a game show?

51:09.540 --> 51:11.220
I know.
It's difficult to explain.

51:11.300 --> 51:12.700
Strange things were happening.

51:12.740 --> 51:14.620
Mmm. So it would appear.

51:14.660 --> 51:16.540
But my life was in danger...

51:16.580 --> 51:18.460
and you saved it.

51:18.500 --> 51:20.860
My heart was beating so fast...

51:20.900 --> 51:22.420
and then it stopped.

51:22.500 --> 51:24.660
And I was just about to die...

51:24.740 --> 51:26.140
and you saved it.

51:26.180 --> 51:28.060
You saved my life.

51:28.100 --> 51:29.980
Well, what are we waiting for?

51:32.020 --> 51:34.740
You want to get on with this
or not?

51:34.780 --> 51:36.300
Sure!

51:36.380 --> 51:38.540
You send the girl over.

51:38.620 --> 51:40.740
Ha ha. First the money.
That was the deal.

51:42.780 --> 51:44.580
Are you OK, Miss Naville?

51:44.660 --> 51:46.380
Yes, I'm OK.

51:46.460 --> 51:48.900
I'm just a little frightened.

52:07.900 --> 52:09.660
Now, don't you worry, miss.

52:09.700 --> 52:12.140
Everything'll be all right.

52:24.500 --> 52:25.620
Well?

52:25.660 --> 52:28.260
Whew. It's here.

52:28.340 --> 52:31.820
OK? Send the girl over.

52:33.180 --> 52:34.700
OK, go on.

52:34.780 --> 52:36.020
Ohh, damn.

52:36.980 --> 52:39.060
Aah! Aah!

52:39.140 --> 52:40.340
Aah! Aah! Help!

52:40.420 --> 52:41.740
Get down! Get down!

52:42.780 --> 52:44.220
Yes.

52:44.300 --> 52:46.420
They tied me up! Ohh!

52:46.500 --> 52:48.500
Ha ha!

53:28.020 --> 53:29.740
Don't move a fucking muscle.

53:32.020 --> 53:33.700
Mmm.

53:34.940 --> 53:36.100
What took you?

53:36.180 --> 53:38.660
He shot up the car!

53:40.580 --> 53:43.460
