why I should dig.

55:02.180 --> 55:03.580
If you dig...

55:04.860 --> 55:06.020
I promise you
when the time comes...

55:06.100 --> 55:07.180
I'll shoot you through the head.

55:08.500 --> 55:10.100
Now, look, you don't like that?

55:10.180 --> 55:11.580
I can just shoot you through
the testicles right now.

55:11.660 --> 55:12.980
You can bleed to death.
I'll dig the grave.

55:13.020 --> 55:15.700
It's up to you.

55:30.580 --> 55:31.900
Can you cut me free?

55:33.180 --> 55:34.860
Please?

55:35.860 --> 55:37.260
It's sore.

