56:21.020 --> 56:22.140
I don't know.

56:24.420 --> 56:26.100
The truth is...

56:26.140 --> 56:29.940
I don't think even he knows
what's going on down here...

56:29.980 --> 56:32.060
the chaos, the...

56:32.140 --> 56:35.340
This hatred, this violence.

56:35.420 --> 56:36.500
Who...

56:37.980 --> 56:39.220
Who are you talking about?

56:42.940 --> 56:44.260
Jeopardy, Jackson...

56:44.340 --> 56:45.740
always works.

56:48.380 --> 56:50.060
Dig.

56:55.100 --> 56:57.940
What are they doing in there?

56:59.180 --> 57:00.900
Should've shot him myself.

57:00.980 --> 57:03.380
Yeah, well, you can't
